Knocked out for a spell. Her systems returned online again. Raising her head, 
she watched Tyrael & Hydras. 

Her optics glanced about. Then she tried to gather some strength, placing her 
hands under her to push herself up. 

She partially got was up... more sitting up, she she was still weak. Slowly 
she would attempt to ragain her strength. Then she needed the CR. Somewhere 
within her.. she still found strength. Holding her side. Moving over to something 
where she hauled herself up onto her feet. Leaning against the object for 
balance. 

Panting, holding her side... she watched Tyrael & Hydras. Then her optics 
glanced around in search for the other Predacons. A couple she did not see.
